{"word":"κυνόπρηστις","slug":"κυνόπρηστις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n60924\" key=\"kuno/prhstis\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κῠνό-πρηστις</orth> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-πρῖστις</foreign> cod.), <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ιδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">πρήθω</etym>) a venomous insect, <sense id=\"n60924.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">whose sting makes dogs swell up</tr_> and die, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βούπρηστις.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}